job.title: Software Engineer Intern
job.description:
Role
The Software Engineer Intern will aid in gathering new neural network frozen graphs, assembling data sets for each graph, and helping to isolate various blocks within the graphs. As part of these roles, you will be expected to work with machine learning frameworks and associated tools. You will be joining a small team in a dynamic startup environment, where each member is expected to take on a wide range of responsibilities and to learn and grow with the company.
Nice to haves
Expected Outcomes in 4 months
